address.streetAddress: Camelot Plan, Plantation Lakes : North Shore Signature Collection

location.fullValue: Camelot Plan, Plantation Lakes : North Shore Signature Collection

data.description: Welcome to resort living in Plantation Lakes a premier amenity rich community.  A 4 bedroom, 4 full bath home with a finished walkout basement , corner lot , granite counters , main level primary bedroom and large back deck, hot tub, and outdoor kitchen for entertaining. Basement has a full bath with washer and dryer hook up and laundry sink, gym area, sewing area, and workshop. The home features granite counters, open kitchen and and family room with fireplace, dining room, living room,  laundry on main floor. There is a primary bedroom on the first floor and an additional bedroom. There are two more bedrooms, a full bath and a sitting area on the second floor   The basement has a fitness room , sewing room , workshop ,  luxurious bathroom with large tile shower, with dual shower heads, sink, hookup for washer and dryer and a laundry sink. Plantation Lakes has two outdoor pools and fitness centers, tennis, basketball court, playground , walking trails and sidewalks, large club house with signature restaurant with bar, and outdoor and indoor dining.  There is an 18 hole Arthur Hills golf course available for residents and open to the public.
